    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 as close to flawless as a used car can get. The exterior paint is brilliant and free of scratches, chips, or swirl marks, with all body panels perfectly aligned and showing no signs of prior damage or repair. The interior is immaculate, with pristine upholstery, spotless carpeting, and all controls and features functioning exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and cleanly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. Service records are up to date, and the car has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. This is a rare opportunity to own a used vehicle that genuinely looks and drives like new.",
