    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in poor condition. The vehicle has noticeable wear throughout \u2014 the interior shows significant deterioration, the exterior has visible damage including scratches and paint issues, and there are mechanical concerns that will require attention. This car has known issues and is priced accordingly. Suitable for buyers comfortable with a project vehicle or those seeking parts.",
