    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Here's a genuinely solid used car that's ready to be your reliable daily driver! This vehicle comes in good condition \u2014 it runs well, handles everyday driving with confidence, and has been honestly maintained. You'll find some normal signs of wear consistent with its age, but nothing that gets in the way of a great ownership experience. If you're looking for a dependable car at a fair price without the premium of a pristine showroom model, this one deserves a serious look. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be pleasantly surprised!",
      "price": 30500.0,
