    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a project car or a budget-friendly fixer-upper? Here's your chance! This vehicle is offered at an honest, no-surprises price that reflects its current condition \u2014 it has seen better days and shows significant wear, both cosmetically and mechanically. It will need meaningful attention and repairs to get it back to its best, so it's ideal for a handy buyer or someone looking for a parts vehicle. What you see is what you get \u2014 priced fairly and sold transparently!",
      "price": 5500.0,
