      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed with full transparency about its condition \u2014 it is in poor shape and priced accordingly. The exterior shows significant wear, including multiple scratches, dents, and paint damage. The interior has notable wear and tear, with damaged upholstery and trim. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will likely require attention, and buyers should plan for repair costs after purchase. This is a project car or parts vehicle suited for a buyer who understands what they're taking on. A pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged. Priced honestly to reflect its true condition.",
      "price": 5500.0,
