    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find \u2014 this vehicle stands as a shining example of what pre-owned perfection looks like. Every inch has been meticulously maintained, from the flawless, blemish-free exterior finish to the spotless, like-new interior that still carries that fresh, refined feel. Mechanically, it performs with the confidence and responsiveness of a vehicle that has been treated with the utmost care throughout its life. Service history is immaculate, and it shows. This is the rare used car that requires absolutely no compromise \u2014 drive it home today with complete peace of mind.",
      "price": 47900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I'm so excited to share this absolute gem with you today. This beauty is truly in showroom-fresh condition \u2014 she turns heads every single time she rolls down the street, and I'm not exaggerating one bit! Every surface gleams, the interior still has that wonderful new-car feel, and she drives like she just rolled off the lot. I've taken incredible pride in keeping her this way, and it really shows. Whether you're treating yourself or looking for that perfect ride to impress, this is the one. She won't last long at this price \u2014 cars like this are rare finds, and I'd love for her to go to someone who'll appreciate her as much as I have. Come take a look \u2014 I promise you won't be disappointed. Let's get you behind the wheel! \ud83d\ude0a",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "2019 Ford Mustang GT Premium \u2014 a true driver's machine presented in exceptional, turn-key condition. Powered by the legendary 5.0L Coyote V8, producing a factory-rated 460 horsepower and 420 lb-ft of torque, mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission with a short-throw feel that enthusiasts demand. The suspension geometry remains tight with zero perceptible play in the steering rack, and all four corners ride on fresh, evenly-worn rubber with substantial tread depth remaining. Paint presents a deep, mirror-like finish with no visible swirl marks under direct lighting \u2014 clearly garaged and detailed with care. Interior surfaces show no stress cracking, no bolster wear, and the infotainment system functions flawlessly across all inputs. Braking hardware inspected and confirmed within spec. This is not a 'driver-quality' example dressed up for sale \u2014 it is a genuinely preserved, mechanically sorted Mustang ready to perform from the moment you leave the lot. Serious inquiries only.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    }
  ],
